      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Over the past few years, I’ve helped start-ups and scale-ups raise millions and turn brands into growth engines. What I’ve learned is simple: "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "great products don’t sell themselves.",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "bold"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "If you're a technical founder or operator, you already know how to build. But with the rise of AI and accessible tooling, building is no longer the hard part. The expectations have shifted. Now, the real challenge is how you think, frame, and distribute."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "This is where systems thinking and marketing become your edge."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Horse to Unicorn",
